comments: Covington (POR) briefly places his hand against Paul's (PHX) side prior to the pick and disengages.
Saric (PHX) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Saric (PHX) initiates contact to Lillard's (POR) body during his drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Saric (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Powell's (POR) path and absorbs the contact.
Powell (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Booker (PHX) before incidental contact occurs.
Powell (POR) loses control of the ball on his way up to the basket and incidental contact occurs with Paul (PHX) as he contests.

Booker (PHX) jumps towards Covington (POR) and makes contact to his back that affects his shot attempt.  The foul is called on Bridges (PHX), who jumps towards Covington and cleanly dislodges the ball and any contact is incidental.
Saric (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in Covington's (POR) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Nurkic (POR) maintains a legal guarding position with a collapsed forearm against Saric's (PHX) side and he absorbs the contact during the shot attempt at the basket.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in Bridges' (PHX) and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
McCollum (POR) makes contact with Saric's (PHX) arm and contact affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Bridges (PHX) moves into Lillard's (POR) path during his drive and he is able to move through the marginal contact.
Lillard (POR) and Bridges (PHX) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Bridges (PHX) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Nurkic (POR) jumps into Bridges' (PHX) body and affects his driving shot attempt before making contact with the ball.
Paul (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Bridges (PHX) places his arm against Lillard's (POR) arm during his drive and removes it prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Booker (PHX) ends his dribble and never loses control of the ball before voluntarily dribbling a second time.
Crowder (PHX) commits a take foul on Covington (POR).
Saric (PHX) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Powell (POR) wraps his arms around Booker (PHX) and the contact affects his FOM.
McCollum (POR) is established in the frontcourt when he deflects the throw-in into the backcourt.  He then illegally gains possession of the ball in the backcourt.
Replay review of the foul called on Powell (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Powell (POR) makes contact with Booker's (PHX) arm and the contact affects his shot attempt.
